57:27.000 --> 57:32.000
I'm not talking about the award for cinema, art, journalism.

57:32.000 --> 57:37.000
There are a lot of awards in business, in various specialties.

57:37.000 --> 57:41.000
Almost every professional community holds certain competitions.

57:41.000 --> 57:44.000
Thus, highlighting the most important people.

57:44.000 --> 57:47.000
The presence of such a certificate on the wall,

57:47.000 --> 57:49.000
if it is paid attention to,

57:49.000 --> 57:53.000
